</screen>
	This shows that an anonymous connection is working.
		</para></step>

		<step><para>
		For your finale, let's try an authenticated connection. Follow this as shown:
<screen>
&rootprompt; smbclient //massive/bobj -Ubobj%n3v3r2l8
