		into the <filename>/etc/samba/</filename> directory. The three files
		should be added together to form the &smb.conf; file.
		</para></step>

		<step><para>
		Follow carefully the steps shown in <link linkend="ch6-bldg1"/>, starting at step 2.
		</para></step>

	</procedure>

